videos.description: Marvin Bagley III goes up strong against two defenders and draws a foul for Duke.
videos.headline: Bagley gets and-1 on double-team

videos.description: Grayson Allen drives and lobs a short ball to Marvin Bagley III for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Allen sets up alley-oop for Bagley

videos.description: Jamar Sandifer drives against Trevon Duval and floats in the basket as he draws the foul against Duke.
videos.headline: Southern's Sandifer floats in and-1

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III swats a ball to half court to meet Grayson Allen who goes behind-the-back to finish the lay-up.
videos.headline: Bagley block followed by Allen skilled finish

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets hit by a reaching Chris Thomas around his eye and goes down.
videos.headline: Allen gets hit by reaching fingers

videos.description: Grayson Allen sells the foul on a hard reach from Torry Mayo who earns a flagrant one.
videos.headline: Allen draws flagrant foul on clothesline

videos.description: Jamar Sandifer launches a high 3-pointer over Grayson Allen for the Jaguars.
videos.headline: Sandifer drains long 3 for Southern

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III misses the scoop but gets his own rebound and jams the putback dunk for Duke.
videos.headline: Bagley slams home putback

videos.description: Javin DeLaurier elevates and pins the ball against the boards for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke's DeLaurier gets a huge block
